= This project is supposed to have these features

1. Landiing Page
   - Option to Login
   - Option to Register & registration process
2. On Login redirect to users page
3. Login page have passowrd gerator

---

Technical Specifications

- React , Redux , Typescript

---

Future Scope of work:

1. Code splitting using 'lazy' and 'suspense'
2. Tree shaking : Using module bundler like webpack to eliminate unused code duiring build process
3. Minification of HTML,CSS, Javascript to reduce unnnecessary whitespace and reduce file size
4. Enable Gzip or brotli on wen server to reduce file size during the transmission
5. Image compression and use WebP , lazy load image on scroeen
6. Enable service worker to enable client side caching and reduce load time on subsequent visits. Cache HCJ to serve them offline
7. code bundling and spplitt8ing
8. Use CSS-in-JS libraries
9. Server side rendering
10. Memoization using React.memo
11. Implement virtualized lists like react-virtualized or react-window
12. API Cacheing
13. Lazy loading and asynchronous data loadin
14. Optimize Images and videos : Use responsive images with the <picture> element or the `scrset` attribute and lazy load image
15. Monitoring usnig Lighthouse , Web Vitals and chrome Devtools Performance latb

